'''Marina Niava''' (wavutse 1985) ni umuyobozi wa firime ya Cote d'Ivoire, utunganya firime, n'umwanditsi.

== Ubuzima bwa Biografiya ==
Niava ni umukobwa muto wa Pierre na Cécile Niava, bombi bigisha indimi. <ref>https://ayanawebzine.com/en-vedette/marina-niava-realisatrice-cineaste-notre-cinema-est-vegetatif-et-ici-il-nexiste-pas-dindustrie-du-cinema/</ref> Yatangiye gukunda ubuhanzi nubuvanganzo kandi yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi byubuvanganzo. Yarangije muri Lycée Sainte Marie d'Abidjan ahabwa igihembo cya Series A Excellence Award. Niava amaze kubona impamyabumenyi ye mu itangazamakuru no gutunganya amajwi n'amashusho yakuye muri Institut des Science et Techniques de la Communication, Niava yatsindiye amarushanwa ayobowe na Radio JAM i Abidjan maze atangira umwuga we nk'umutoza. Nyuma yaje kuba umunyamakuru muri Afurika 24. <ref name="cineaste">https://www.abidjan.net/qui/profil.asp?id=981</ref> Niava yateje imbere sinema mugihe cyo gufata amashusho yamamaza. <ref name="topsuccess">https://web.archive.org/web/20160229053440/https://www.africatopsuccess.com/2014/08/12/marina-niava-la-cineaste-ivoirienne-qui-perce-aux-usa/</ref>

Kuva mu 2009 kugeza 2010, Niava yabaye umwanditsi umwe mu gihembwe cya 1 cya ''serivise Teenager'', yakiriye igihembo cy’uruhererekane rwiza rwa Afurika mu iserukiramuco rya Vues d'Afrique ryabereye i Montreal. Yimukiye i Oslo, muri Noruveje mu 2010 aba umuyobozi ushinzwe itumanaho mu kigo ndangamuco nyafurika. Niava yagenzuye ibirori bya firime ya Kino Afrika 2010 na 2011 muri Oslo.  Yabaye igihembo cya BENIANH International Foundation cyatsindiye igihembo cya buruse muri 2012. <ref>https://news.abidjan.net/h/624792.html</ref>

Mu Kwakira 2012, yayoboye documentaire ye ya mbere, ''Noirs au soleil levant'', ivuga ku buzima bw’abanyeshuri bo muri Afurika i Tsukuba, mu Buyapani. Filime ya mbere ya Niava ngufi, ''21'', yarangiye mu Kuboza 2013.  Yatewe inkunga n'amafaranga yatanzwe n'Umuryango mpuzamahanga de la Francophonie. <ref>https://www.lemonde.fr/afrique/article/2018/02/28/television-les-series-africaines-crevent-l-ecran_5263576_3212.html</ref> ''21'' ivuga kubyerekeye umukobwa ukiri muto udashobora kwihanganira umukunzi wa nyina kandi niwe filime yonyine yo muri Afrika yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Oakland. Niava yarayoboye gito mahano ''Worse'' muri 2014.  Yakoze nkumuhuzabikorwa wihariye wa firime ''Advantageous'' 2015. <ref>https://www.commdev.org/young-media-professionals/#toggle-id-5</ref>

Niava yarangije icyiciro cya gatatu cya kaminuza cya Filime na Televiziyo muri Academy ya Art University . <ref>http://pressecotedivoire.ci/article/3918-portraitmarina-niava-ecrivaine-et-cineaste-dans-lame</ref> Muri 2017, Niava yanditse igitabo cye cya mbere, ''American Dreamer''. Yabaye finale ya 10 Prix Ivoire pour la Littérature Africaine d'Expression Francophone. <ref>https://lifemag-ci.com/la-liste-des-ouvrages-finalistes-du-prix-ivoire-2017/</ref>

== Igice cya firime ==

* 2009-2010: ''Umwangavu'' (urukurikirane rwa TV, dufatanije kwandika)
* 2012: ''Noirs au soleil levant'' (film ngufi, umuyobozi)
* 2013: ''21'' (film ngufi, umwanditsi / umuyobozi)
* 2014: ''Ikibi'' (film ngufi, umwanditsi / umuyobozi)

